WEBVTT

00:00.227 --> 00:02.553
Officially the smallest mobile phone in the world,...

00:03.307 --> 00:05.032
...meet the Zanco Tiny T1.

00:05.907 --> 00:06.053
Hello?

00:06.466 --> 00:10.039
This fully-functioning talk and text mobile phone is unbelievably tiny.

00:11.853 --> 00:14.337
It's the must-have novelty gift for any gadget lover.

00:15.638 --> 00:17.221
It's smaller than your thumb.

00:17.638 --> 00:20.405
It's lighter than a coin and it is ridiculously cute.

00:21.573 --> 00:24.730
The first time you see it, you can't believe it exists.

00:25.214 --> 00:27.041
Your second thought is, "Does it work?"

00:28.147 --> 00:31.050
Use the Tiny T1 as a backup or emergency phone...

00:31.311 --> 00:34.005
...that you can keep in your bag, pocket or glove compartment.

